  FinalMacros.Guide.info
  FinalMacrosD.Guide
  FinalMacrosD.Guide.info
  ENV_Locale
  Macros/                     
    Text2Block.rexx         \\
    ResizeObject.rexx       |
    StretchObjects.rexx     |
    SizeNOblique.rexx       | by NDY's
    FinalWaver.rexx         |
    ExpandObjects.rexx      |
    CentreObjects.rexx      |
    Shadow.rexx             /
